": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010139, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon the Prophetic Tree and the Hashemite plant that is luminous, fruitful of Prophethood, and elegant with Imamate. And [peace be] upon your two grave-fellows; Adam and Noah, peace be upon both of them. Peace be upon you and upon your Household, the pure and immaculate. Peace be upon you and upon the angels surrounding you and encompassing your tomb.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho nabuwat ke shajra’e tayyaba par aur bani-haashim ke darakht'e karam par jo noorani hai aur jo nabuwat ka hal-phal dene waala hai aur jo imamat se aaraasta hai aur salaam ho aap ke pehlu mein aaraam farmane waale Janabe Aadam (a.s) aur Janabe Nooh (a.s) par. Salaam ho aap par aur aap ke paak o paakeeza Ahlebait (a.s) par, Salaam ho aap par aur aap ke ird-gird malaayeka aur qabr ke paas maujood farishto’n par. Ay mere maula, ay Amirul Momeneen yeh Yek-Shamba (Sunday) ka din hai jo aap ka din hai aur aap ke naam se mansoob hai aur mai is din aap ka mehmaan hu aur aap ki panah mein hu.", "Urdu": "درخشاں شجرۂ نبویہ اور گلزار ہاشمیہ پر سلام ہو جو نبوت سے ثمرآور ہوا ہے اور امامت سے لہرایا ہے۔ اور آدمؑ و نوح ؑ پر سلام ہو جو آپ کے پاس دفن ہیں۔ آپ پر سلام ہو اور آپ کے اہل بیتؑ پر جو پاک و پاکیزہ ہیں۔ آپ پر سلام ہو اوران فرشتوں پر جو آپ کے دروازے پر کھڑے ہیں اور آپ کی قبر کو گھیرے ہوئے ہیں اے میرے مولاؑ اے مومنوں کے امیر!یہ اتوار کا دن ہے اور یہی آپ کا دن ہے اور آپ کے نام سے منسوب ہے اور میں اس دن میں آپ کا مہمان اور آپ کی پناہ میں ہوں۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LASH SHAJARATIN NABAWIYYATE WAD DAWHATIL HAASHEMIYYATIL MOZEE-ATIL MUSMERATE BIN NOBUWWATIL MOONEQATE BIL EMAAMATE WA A’LAA ZAJEEA’YKA AADAMA WA NOOHIN A’LAYHEMAS SALAAMO ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA WA A’LAA AHLE BAYTEKAT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA WA A’LAL MALAAAEKATIL MOHDEQEENA BEKA WAL HAAAF-FEENA BE QABREKA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَی الشَّجَرَۃِ النَّبَوِیَّۃِ وَالدَّوْحَۃِ الْھَاشِمِیَّۃِ الْمُضِیْئَۃِ الْمُثْمِرَۃِ بِالنُّبُوَّۃِ الْمُوْنِقَۃِ بِالْاِمَامَۃِ وَعَلٰی ضَجِیْعَیْکَ آدَمَ وَنُوْحٍ عَلَیْھِمَاالسَّلَامُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکَ وَعَلٰی اَھْلِ بَیْتِکَ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاھِرِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْکَ وَعَلَی الْمَلَآئِکَۃِ الْمُحْدِقِیْنَ بِکَ وَالْحَافِّیْنَ بِقَبْرِکَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010354, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O my master, O Commander of the Believers! Today is Sunday, which is your day and carrying your name, and, on this day, I am your guest and in your vicinity; therefore, my master, receive me as your guest and neighbor. Surely, you are generous and hospitable and you are commanded to treat your neighbors hospitably. So, (please) do to me that which I desire from you and I hope you to do, [I ask you] in the name of your and your Household’s standing with Allah and His standing with you all, and in the name of your cousin, Allah’s Messenger, may Allah’s peace and blessings be upon him and upon them all.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay mere maula aap mujhe mehmaan bana lijiye aur mujhe panah dijiye keh aap karim hai aur mehmaan-daari ko pasand karte hai aur panah dene par maamur hai to aap mere liye is Yek-Shamba (Sunday) mein woh kaam kar dijiye jiski taraf meri raghbat hai aur jiski mai aap se ummeed rakhta hu. Aap ko, aap aur aap ke ghar waalo’n ki is manzelat ka waasta jo Allah ke yahan aap ka martaba hai. aur aap ki nighah mein jo Khuda ka maqaam hai us maqaam aur aap ke chacha-zaad bhai ke haq ka waasta jo Allah ke Rasool hai “Un par aur unki Aal par Allah ki rehmat naazil ho aur sab par salaam ho”.", "Urdu": "اب میرے مولا ؑ مجھے مہمان کیجیے اور پناہ دیجیے کہ بے شک آپ سخی، مہمان نواز اور پناہ دینے پر مامور ہیں۔ لہٰذا جس مقصد سے میں اس دن حا ضر ہوا ہوں اور آپ سے جو آرزو رکھتا ہوں پوری فرمائیے اپنی اور اپنے خاندان کی خداکے ہاں بلندی کے واسطے اور خدا کی منزلت کے واسطے جو آپ کے نزدیک ہے اور اپنے چچا کے بھائی حضرت رسول ؐکے حق کے واسطے میری آرزو پوری کیجیے آنحضرتؐ اور ان سب پر درودو سلام ہو۔", "RArabic": "YAA MAWLAAYA YAA AMEERAL MOMINEENA HAAZAA YAWMUL AHADE WA HOWA YAWMOKA WA BISMEKA WA ANAA ZAYFOKA FEEHE WA JAAROKA FA AZIFNEE YAA MAWLAAYA WA AJIRNEE FA INNAKA KAREEMUN TOHIBBUZ ZEYAAFATE WA MAAMOORUN BIL EJAARATE FAF-A’L MAA RAGHIBTO ELAYKA FEEHE WA RAJAWTOHU MINKA BE MANZELATEKA WA AALE BAYTEKA I’NDALLAAHE WA MANZELATEHI I’NDAKUM WA BEHAQQIBNE A’MMEKA RASOOLIL LAAHE SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI WA SALLAMA WA A’LAYHIM AJMAE’EN.", "ArabicText1": "یَامَوْلَایَ یَااَمِیْرَالْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ ھَذٰا یَوْمُ الْاَحَدِ وَھُوَ یَوْمُکَ وَبِاسْمِکَ وَاَنَا ضَیْفُکَ فِیْہِ وَجَارُکَ فَاَضِفْنِیْ یَامَوْلَایَ وَاَجِرْنِیْ فَاِنَّکَ کَرِیْمٌ تُحِبُّ الضِّیَاْفَۃَ وَمَامُوْرٌ بِالْاِجَارَۃِ فَافْعَلْ مَا رَغِبْتُ اِلَیْکَ فِیْہِ وَرَجَوْتُہٗ مِنْکَ بِمَنْزِلَتِکَ وَاٰلِ بَیْتِکَ عِنْدَاللہِ وَمَنْزِلَتِہٖ عِنْدَکُمْ وَبِحَقِّ ابْنِ عَمِّکَ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ صَلَّی اللہُ عَلَیْہِ وَاٰلِہٖ وَسَلَّمَ وَعَلَیْھِمْ اَجْمَعِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "Arabi